Just because Mao isn't pick/ban status doesn't mean tanks are garbage now. This is the same problem we had with getting rid of the ADC monopoly on bot lane. ADCs weren't 90% of the top 10 picks so they were suddenly "garbage," despite the fact that 3 of the top 5 bot picks were ADCs, and 6 of the top 10 bot picks were ADCs. Then they got massive re-buffs that all but reverted the crit changes.
